# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenTofu / Terraform
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# State 檔案：含專案 ID、實際配發的 IP、user-data 等敏感細節，絕不進版控
# State files: contain project ID, provisioned IPs, user-data and other
# sensitive details — must never be committed
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Provider 外掛與本機快取：體積大且可透過 `tofu init` 重新下載
# Provider plugins and local cache: large, and re-downloadable via `tofu init`
.terraform/

# 變數值檔案：屬環境特定內容，請改用 terraform.tfvars.example 作為範本
# Variable value files: environment-specific — use terraform.tfvars.example
# as a template instead
*.tfvars

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# 注意 / Note
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# .terraform.lock.hcl 應「保留」並納入版控，以鎖定 provider 版本、確保可重現性
# .terraform.lock.hcl should be KEPT and committed — it pins provider
# versions to guarantee reproducible builds
